Class DynaBeanAdapter

java.lang.Object
  org.azeckoski.reflectutils.beanutils.DynaBeanAdapter
All Implemented Interfaces:
FieldAdapter
public class DynaBeanAdapter
extends Object
implements FieldAdapter

This allows dynabeans to work with the field utils, should only be loaded by reflection if the DynaBean class can be found

Author:
Aaron Zeckoski (azeckoski @ gmail.com)
